-- Hitachi, Johnson Controls to Ally on Energy Storage, Lithium-Ion Batteries
-- B y   K y u n g   B o k   C h o
-- 2010-10-18T00:04:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/hitachi-johnson-controls-to-ally-on-energy-storage-lithium-ion-batteries.html
Hitachi Ltd. and Johnson Controls
Inc. will cooperate on energy storage, including the development
and production of lithium-ion batteries, according to a joint
statement today on PR Newswire.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kyung Bok Cho at 
 kcho7@bloomberg.net  